txt.en: The stone-giant Helf has stolen the egg of a Great Eagle. He has retreated back to the safety of his mountain home upon Iorbar's Peak, where he plans to make the egg into his next meal.
Complete the quest Iorbar's Peak -- Tier 2
You must protect the egg from Helf's devious ambitions and return it to the possession of the Eagles.
